{"id":572160,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【图说天朝】天津最美图书馆-用假书装点门面/","date":"2017-11-17T07:08:08Z","modified":"2017-11-17T07:08:08Z","title":"【图说天朝】天津“最美图书馆” 用假书装点门面","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>法新社驻京记者 Rebecca Davis (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rebeccaludavis/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@rebeccaludavis</a>) 近日探访了官媒热炒的天津滨海“最美图书馆”，结果她震惊地发现，虽然乍看之下摆满书籍，但这座光鲜亮丽、设计充满未来感的图书馆书架上的书，绝大多数都是“假书”，是金属版上用来装饰的背景。</p>\n<p>根据<a href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/news/chinas-futuristic-library-more-fiction-books-093019395.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">法新社报道</a>，在荷兰建筑公司 MVRDV 的原始设计中，场馆中间开放空间内的一层层书架上是用来摆放书籍的，但天津滨海图书馆副馆长刘秀峰称<strong>政府最终没有批准这项用途</strong>，所以现在这块空间只能用来让人进行读书、休息、交流活动，现在开放空间内展示的少量书籍可能很快就要撤走。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_572169\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-572169\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"621\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library.jpg 1002w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library-253x300.jpg 253w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library-768x909.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library-865x1024.jpg 865w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">“太令人伤心了，这华丽的阅读室里的书绝大多数都不是真的！只是书架上印了书而已”；@rebeccaludavis 推特截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_572167\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-572167\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/DOze7hLU8AAzg61-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">书架上的“书”；图片来自 Twitter @rebeccaludavis</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_572170\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-572170\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2.jpg 1278w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2-300x231.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2-768x593.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/tianjin-library2-1024x790.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">“然而，这些六个语言版本的习近平的书，倒都是真的”；@rebeccaludavis 推特截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[13016,9346,11848]}